I made an animated version of  my winter cover for @columbiamagazine to be used on their website and newsletter. This was so much fun to work on! ✨ I was an animation double major in college and recently been missing making images move, I hope to be doing more of that! ✨ (Ps This is not the music they used, I didn't have it on my end 😊)
Thanks again to wonderful AD @lenpsmall and the whole team!

