Who’s coming to paint in Italy with me this Fall? 🎨🖌️🇮🇹 I’m collaborating with the amazing Danielle Oteri from @feastonhistory to bring you an artist retreat in Southern Italy, the most magical place on earth. The retreat will run October 22-29 2023, where we will stay at the amazing @borgolapietraia_countryhouse and soak up inspiration from the Cilento Coast.
We will paint, eat, drink wine, and learn about the history and art of the region. No prior art experience needed, just the desire to draw, paint and enjoy beautiful things! Click the link in my bio for more info and to register! Ciao! 🎨🖌️🇮🇹

