I can't believe that tomorrow is my last full day at @borgolapietraia and my last day to hang out with my Italian sister @aryscar 😭 I hope I can come back soon, maybe as soon as Spring 2024, with all of you , in our next Italian retreat! Join us May 19-26 2024!  🇮🇹
@feastonhistory and I are leading our tours here in the Cilento coast, the tour has painting, drawing, art history, food and wine, and even birds! 🐦🖌️ All levels welcome. 
Click the link in my bio for more details, and I hope to see you there! ⛵ 

